Subject: So This is Your First Penguicon...
Description: So it's your first time! One of us! One of us! Great, now that you're here, how do you do it right? What's up with the ribbons? How do you pick what you want do when soooomg many things are going on? Where's the free beer? What happened to the brazilian beef? Why is hand sanitizer terrible salad dressing? Learn some survival tips and hear some heart-warming stories from some seasoned experts, previous conchairs, and convention organizers!  Speakers include:Cassy Sinke, Lithie Dubois, Janet Gocay, Scott Kennedy, Jessica Ann Roland, Nuri Gocay - Track: Penguicon  - Duration: 1 hour
